Title: 整体架构图
Describe: S04_ARCHITECTURE。展示 monorepo 的层级架构、依赖方向和运行时边界。
------------------------------------------------------------
[Example]
分层架构

[Description]
LangChain 的架构核心是“稳定抽象层 + 用户 API 层 + provider 适配层 + 测试契约层”。Core 不应该依赖上层包；上层包和 provider 通过 Core 接口协作。

[UML]
@startuml
top to bottom direction
package "应用代码" as App {
  component "create_agent / chains / runnables" as AppAPI
}
package "LangChain API 层" as API {
  component "langchain v1" as V1
  component "langchain_classic" as Classic
}
package "Core 抽象层" as CoreLayer {
  component "Runnable" as Runnable
  component "BaseChatModel" as BaseChatModel
  component "BaseTool" as BaseTool
  component "Messages / Documents" as MessagesDocs
}
package "实现与适配层" as Impl {
  component "partners/*" as Partners
  component "text-splitters" as Splitters
}
package "质量与数据层" as Quality {
  component "standard-tests" as Tests
  component "model-profiles" as Profiles
}

AppAPI --> V1
AppAPI --> Classic
V1 --> CoreLayer
Classic --> CoreLayer
Partners --> CoreLayer
Splitters --> CoreLayer
Tests --> Partners
Tests --> CoreLayer
Profiles --> Partners
@enduml

[Detail]
入口从应用代码开始，通常进入 `langchain` v1 或 classic API，再落到 Core 抽象。Provider 适配层不能反向污染 Core，否则会破坏独立发布和通用接口。`standard-tests` 对 provider 和 Core 行为做契约检查，`model-profiles` 为 partner 数据补充模型能力。修改 Core 公共方法时，影响会沿图中所有向下依赖扩散。

------------------------------------------------------------
[Example]
包发布与依赖约束

[Description]
独立包通过版本范围连接。比如 `langchain` v1 依赖 `langchain-core>=1.4.0,<2.0.0` 和 `langgraph>=1.2.3,<1.3.0`；OpenAI partner 依赖 `langchain-core`、`openai` 和 `tiktoken`。

[UML]
None

[Detail]
这种发布架构的好处是 provider 可以较快升级服务 SDK，而 Core 保持抽象稳定。代价是版本范围、editable source 和标准测试必须同步维护。新增 partner 不只是新增代码目录，还要更新 CI label、release、issue template、dependabot、PR lint scope 等基础设施清单。

